.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
A tiny script for creating websites with \f[C]pandoc\f[].
.SS Options
.PP
\f[B]\-b\f[] Builds site.
.PP
\f[B]\-l\f[] Indexes the \f[C]BLOGDIR\f[] and creates
\f[C]$BLOGDIR/index.md\f[].
.PP
\f[B]\-d\f[] Starts http server (\f[C]httpwatcher\f[]) and watch daemon
(\f[C]entr\f[]).
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
\ \ \ \ Builds\ site\ on\ file\ change\ in\ `SRCDIR`\ and\ `STATICDIR`.
\f[]
.fi
